          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "title": "What is your late policy?",
            "content": "<p>We appreciate your punctuality. We offer a 15-minute grace period for your arrival. After 15 minutes, your appointment may be rescheduled or your time slot might get given to the next client waiting.</p><p>Please let us know if you're running late so we can try our best to accommodate you.</p>"
